{{wikipedia}}
==English==
===Noun===
'''earwig''' (''plural'' '''earwigs''')

# Any of various [[insect]]s of the order ''[[Dermaptera]]'' that have elongated bodies, large membraneous wings folded underneath short leathery forewings and a pair of large pincers protruding from the rear of the [[abdomen]].

====Scientific names====
*[[Forficula auricularia]] (''common earwig'')

